## Brand Guidelines

### Do's
- ✅ Always include specific, credible details
- ✅ Ask engaging questions to build community
- ✅ Balance medical terminology with accessible language
- ✅ Share tools and systems openly
- ✅ Acknowledge both struggle and strength
- ✅ Use consistent hashtag strategy
- ✅ Maintain professional but personal boundaries

### Don'ts
- ❌ Never inspiration porn or toxic positivity  
- ❌ Don't minimize others' experiences
- ❌ Avoid giving specific medical advice
- ❌ Don't use ableist language or imagery
- ❌ Never compromise on accessibility standards
- ❌ Don't share without proper medical disclaimers

